### 1. Create two fake players
# (Je maakt deze zelf aan in je app, maar hier gewoon UUID’s)
@playerX = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@playerO = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222

### 2. Create game
POST http://localhost:8086/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "players": [
    "{{playerX}}",
    "{{playerO}}"
  ],
  "settings": {
    "boardSize": 3
  }
}

> {% client.global.set("gameId", response.body.id); %}

### 3. Get game state
GET http://localhost:8086/api/games/{{gameId}}

### MOVE SEQUENCE
# Win condition: X plays (0,0) (0,1) (0,2)

### 4. Move 1 — X plays top-left
POST http://localhost:8086/api/games/{{gameId}}/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "playerId": "{{playerX}}",
  "row": 0,
  "col": 0
}

### 5. Move 2 — O plays random
POST http://localhost:8086/api/games/{{gameId}}/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "playerId": "{{playerO}}",
  "row": 1,
  "col": 1
}

